    <title>Pool configuration parameters</title>
    <body>
      <p>The memory pools can be configured, both with the DDS_set_pool_constraints() function (see:
        Configuring memory pools) as well as with Pool configuration parameters.</p>
      <p>Following parameters are defined:</p>
      <p>
        <table frame="all" rowsep="1" colsep="1" id="table_vcg_fnt_r4">
          <title>Pool configuration parameters</title>
